               <head>Khazin al-Shu'ara'</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Taz̲kirah-'i khāzin al-shuʿarāʾ by ʿAlī Kabīr Mīranjān Ilāhābādī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85014152 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85100084" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_3899-item1">
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656364.0x000001 viaf_137972961">ʿAlī Kabīr Mīranjān Ilāhābādī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" type="alt" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656364.0x000001 viaf_137972961">على كبير ميرنجان اله آبادى </persName>
                     </author>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Alternative title: <term xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc">Vāqiʿāt al-nādirāt</term>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                           <term xml:lang="en">Dictionary</term> of alphabetically-arranged biographical notices for 191 north Indian poets of <term xml:lang="en">Persian</term>, by ʿAlī Kabīr al-mawʿid Mīranjān al-Ḥusaynī al-Muḥammadī al-Ḥanafī al-Naqshbandī al-Abū al-ʿAlā-yi Ilāhābādī, largely drawn from the <name type="place">Ilāhābād</name> (<name type="place">Allahabad</name>) region (<name type="place">Uttar Pradesh</name>, <name type="place">India</name>) 
                        </p>
                        <p>Separate list of headings and subheadings appended to the start (ff. i-iv)</p>
                        <p>Possibly the author's <term xml:lang="en">autograph</term> copy, written for or at the behest of <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f7737" role="pat">Sayyid Muḥammad Bashīr</persName>, called <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f7669" role="pat">Abū al-Qāsim Muḥammad</persName>
                        </p>
                        <p>Further described in Storey's entry in Persian Literature (vol. 1, part 2, pp. 902-3)</p>
                     </note>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21905">Taz̲kirah-'i khāzin al-shuʿarāʾ</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_21905">تذكرهٴ خازن الشّعراٴ</title>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
